---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="PulseStack Pricing – Simple, Usage-Based Plans"
  description="Start free, then scale PulseStack as your team and customer signal grow."
>
  
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 py-16 space-y-8">
    <div class="max-w-2xl space-y-3">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-50">
        Simple, usage-based pricing.
      </h1>
      <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-slate-300">
        Start with a free trial. When you’re ready, choose a plan that fits your stage — without annual lock-in or surprise overages.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1.2fr)_minmax(0,1fr)]">
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-indigo-500/60 bg-slate-900/80 p-6 shadow-xl shadow-indigo-500/30">
        <p class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-indigo-300 mb-2">
          Growth
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-baseline gap-2 mb-3">
          <span class="text-3xl font-semibold text-slate-50">$99</span>
          <span class="text-xs text-slate-400">/month</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-300 mb-4">
          For SaaS product teams that want AI-powered insight across 3–5 core tools.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-xs text-slate-200 mb-5">
          <li>✔ Up to 5 data sources</li>
          <li>✔ 50k feedback items analyzed / month</li>
          <li>✔ Impact simulation reports</li>
          <li>✔ Slack + email alerts</li>
          <li>✔ Priority chat support</li>
        </ul>
        <a
          href="#"
          class="inline-flex w-full items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-indigo-500 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-slate-950 hover:bg-indigo-400 transition"
        >
          Start free trial
        </a>
        <p class="mt-3 text-[11px] text-slate-400">
          14-day free trial · No credit card required · Cancel anytime
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/70 p-6 text-sm space-y-3">
        <h2 class="font-medium text-slate-50">Need enterprise features?</h2>
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-300">
          We offer dedicated SLAs, SSO/SAML, advanced permissions, and deployment options for regulated industries.
        </p>
        <a href="/faq" class="text-xs text-indigo-300 hover:text-indigo-200 underline underline-offset-4">
          Learn more and talk to sales →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
